Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.14,0:22:18.94,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}視界に目前映る深い真紅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.82,0:22:29.08,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}この先およそ 40000km
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:36.50,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}後ろに迫る互いの傷が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.83,0:22:41.71,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}迷う道をさらに迷わせてく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.71,0:22:46.09,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}見えず匂わぬ、違えぬ未来が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.39,0:22:48.30,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}背中を突いた！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:49.43,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}だから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.43,0:22:57.94,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}今日の夜は隣にいさせて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.06,0:23:06.86,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}今夜だけは本気だからね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.12,0:23:10.58,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}こっちにきてもっと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.58,0:23:12.91,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}祈りあった未来とて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:14.87,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}道が違うのよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.87,0:23:16.71,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}アナタ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.09,0:23:22.46,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}互いの殺意で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.46,0:23:25.84,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}トドメ喰らっちゃうね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.26,0:23:30.47,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}やっぱりやめとくわ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.14,0:22:18.94,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}映入視野的深邃緋紅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.82,0:22:29.08,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}前方大約還有40000km
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.08,0:22:36.50,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}緊追過來的彼此的傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.83,0:22:41.71,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}讓迷茫的路途再添迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.71,0:22:46.09,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}不可視不可聞的唯一未來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.39,0:22:48.30,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}從背後一擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.30,0:22:49.43,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}所以說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.43,0:22:57.94,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}今夜請讓我伴你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.06,0:23:06.86,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}只有今夜我無比認真
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.12,0:23:10.58,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}再靠過來一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.58,0:23:12.91,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}縱然我們一同祈願的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.91,0:23:14.87,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}前路也會分岔而行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.87,0:23:16.71,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}親愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.09,0:23:22.46,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}讓我們傾盡彼此的殺意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.46,0:23:25.84,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}給予對方最後一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.26,0:23:30.47,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)\blur3}果然還是算了吧
Comment: 0,0:00:01.00,0:00:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
